<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_417_r1l11"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> / Es ıſt cʒü vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> Hans <expan>Spring<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Römhılt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l12">mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Graf <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Henne<ex>n</ex>b<ex>er</ex>g</expan> briefe der vns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l13">Hanſen vnd <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ſeinen <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / als Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l14"><expan>newlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etlıch Jr habe auf <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> walde gen <expan>Erlang<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l15"> <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ıſt / 
