<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l16">als wir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . Nu ſprıcht <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> hans / daʒ er <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l17"><expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Henne<ex>n</ex>b<ex>er</ex>g</expan> auch einen brief an ew hab / vnd </ab>
