<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, es ist czü uns
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> Hans <expan>Spring<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Römhilt mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> graf <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Henne<ex>n</ex>b<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, briefe, der uns
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Hansen und
                            <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> seinen <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, als in
                                <expan>newlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etlich ir habe auf
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> walde gen
                            <expan>Erlang<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist, <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> etlich
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> knechte verdacht sind, als wir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Nu spricht <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Hans, daz er <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Henne<ex>n</ex>b<ex>er</ex>g</expan> auch einen brief an ew hab, und
                        also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dar czü fürderlich und
                                <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein wöllet, ob in das ir
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>werd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> möchte.</ab>
</div>
